2
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:13,090
<i>and prepare breakfast and baby food.</i>

3
00:00:13,740 --> 00:00:16,270
<i>Then I'd wake Hiroki and Shiori up.</i>

4
00:00:16,270 --> 00:00:20,450
Hang on, hang on, hang on...

5
00:00:21,850 --> 00:00:24,920
- Where did it go?
<i>- I'd change her diapers,</i>

6
00:00:24,920 --> 00:00:27,960
<i>- sweep the floor,</i>
- Oops, sorry...

7
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,950
<i>wash the dishes,</i>

