11
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:47,050
<i>have a quick lunch,</i>

12
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:48,960
<i>go to the supermarket,</i>

13
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:50,330
<i>and prepare dinner.</i>

14
00:00:50,330 --> 00:00:52,090
Good day. I'm from Angel-Sitter.

15
00:00:52,090 --> 00:00:54,220
I look forward to looking after your baby today.

16
00:00:54,220 --> 00:00:55,350
Thank you.

17
00:00:55,350 --> 00:00:58,640
- I'm still not quite done yet. Sorry about that.
- No problem.

18
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:03,290
<i>All this time, I would spend my entire day</i>

19
00:01:03,290 --> 00:01:06,000
<i>with Shiori by my side every single moment.</i>

20
00:01:08,270 --> 00:01:10,960
<i>But right now,</i>

21
00:01:11,750 --> 00:01:14,110
<i>what am I supposed to do?</i>

22
